<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870506-0017 </DOCNO><HL> Business Brief:MCI Communications Corp.</HL><DD> 05/06/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> MCIC </IN><TEXT>   MCI COMMUNICATIONS CORP., Washington, said shareholders at its annual meeting approved an amendment to the company's certificate of incoporation that limits the personal liability of directors as allowed under Delaware law. Holders of the telecommunications concern also cleared indemnification agreements with directors. </TEXT></DOC>